preference.name: Architecture_generic_id_mapping
preference.preference_description: Specifies the composite property used for initial mapping of the object property to the generic component Id of the part. This will be used to pre-populate the component id in the Add part to product wizard. Format for this preference is : <Architecture_Type>_generic_id_mapping.
